<p>Based on an idea that came up while I was writing ‘The Night Beach’ for the Jam Contest. Thanks to DarkStuff, not_a_seagull, StormmCreeper, Phantom, thewalkindude368, PeppersGhost, Kakroom, GibberingEloquence, CaptainKirby, TheGreatSea, NineVolt, LordStonefish, Tufto, Rimple, Ihpkmn, magnadeus, DarkStuff again and PeppersGhost again.</p>
<p>Surprise! It’s an 001 Proposal! I had one of these before, but it became a mainlist skip shortly after. I started writing this as a mainlist skip, but now it’s an 001. It’s like poetry &#8212; it rhymes.</p>

