			<div class="content" id="post-content-3718262">
									

<p>Holy crap.</p>
<p>As a rule of thumb, I usually never make my skips <em>longer</em>, because it usually just leads to them dragging on. It's a rule I suggest to everybody. However, this, <em>holy crap</em>, this is the exception to that rule. I was on the edge of my seat the entire time.</p>
<p>Amazing work, getting your 001 to work while I couldn't. I might actually have to reconsider my top 10 list now.</p>
<p>+1</p>

