			<div class="content" id="post-content-3718678">
									

<p>&quot;&#8230;this reduces the O5 council to the Injustice League.&quot;</p>
<p>I have mixed feelings on this criticism. On one hand, I enjoy stories where the Foundation is portrayed sympathetically. I've even written a story where the O5 Council come off sympathetically myself. So I definitely understand the appeal.</p>
<p>On the other hand&#8230; the Foundation is massive underground intelligence agency with no public accountability whatsoever. The FBI and the CIA have pulled off a lot of shady shit with no real consequences to them, and they each had at least some public accountability. And they're already complicit in thousands of counts of kidnapping, murder, human experimentation&#8230; so yeah, I can definitely see them talking themselves into this.</p>
<p>(P.S. Love your work Hippo. Especially SCP-3054.)</p>

							</div>

								
					
